sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant System as System
    participant Recipient as Recipient

    User->>System: Send self-destructing message
    System->>Recipient: Deliver message
    Recipient->>System: Read message
    System->>Recipient: Start timer for self-destruction
    Note right of System: Timer expires
    System->>Recipient: Delete message
    System->>User: Confirm message deletion